    <item>
      <title>金正恩称随着与俄罗斯关系加深，经济呈现“好转”态势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/kim-jong-un-says-economy-is-on-upturn-as-russian-ties-deepen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜领导人金正恩表示，朝鲜经济正在“明显好转”，朝鲜宣布成功试射了一枚新型战术弹道导弹，朝鲜可以将此枚导弹运往俄罗斯，以换取俄罗斯帮助朝鲜政权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/kim-jong-un-says-economy-is-on-upturn-as-russian-ties-deepen</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 02:06:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在赢得豁免权后寻求推翻纽约重罪判决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/trump-seeks-to-toss-ny-felony-conviction-after-immunity-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院裁定唐纳德·特朗普因其担任总统期间的行为而享有实质上的刑事起诉豁免权后，特朗普正努力争取撤销其在纽约的封口费定罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/trump-seeks-to-toss-ny-felony-conviction-after-immunity-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 00:15:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡将收紧赌场监管以打击恐怖主义融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/singapore-to-tighten-casino-rules-to-counter-terrorism-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡将降低赌场现金存款检查的门槛，以防止恐怖分子和犯罪组织利用这一机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/singapore-to-tighten-casino-rules-to-counter-terrorism-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 23:17:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯取消助长房地产繁荣的住房抵押贷款补贴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/russia-ends-housing-mortgage-subsidy-that-stoked-a-property-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯正在逐步取消一项成本高昂的抵押贷款补贴计划，该计划在新冠疫情和乌克兰战争期间曾助长房地产繁荣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/russia-ends-housing-mortgage-subsidy-that-stoked-a-property-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>惠特默表示她 100% 支持拜登，否认紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/whitmer-says-she-s-100-behind-biden-dismissing-talk-of-tension</link>
      <description><![CDATA[密歇根州州长格雷琴·惠特默表示，她很自豪支持总统乔·拜登成为民主党候选人，并反驳了有关拜登在上周辩论中遇到困难后她的团队与拜登竞选团队之间存在紧张关系的说法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/whitmer-says-she-s-100-behind-biden-dismissing-talk-of-tension</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 21:46:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党考虑在 7 月中旬投票正式推选拜登为总统候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/democrats-weigh-early-biden-nomination-to-squash-talk-of-a-swap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党全国委员会正考虑最早在 7 月中旬正式提名乔·拜登，以确保总统能够出现在 11 月的选票上，同时有助于消除在上周辩论表现不佳后党内关于更换他的传言。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/democrats-weigh-early-biden-nomination-to-squash-talk-of-a-swap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 19:11:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登抨击法院对特朗普转移年龄焦点的裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/trump-s-immunity-win-also-helps-biden-distract-from-debate-mess</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登呼吁选民对唐纳德·特朗普“作出判断”。此前，最高法院的一项裁决为这位共和党总统候选人可能逃脱因其在 1 月 6 日美国国会大厦骚乱中所扮演的角色而受到的起诉铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/trump-s-immunity-win-also-helps-biden-distract-from-debate-mess</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 18:00:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界银行启动担保额度增至 200 亿美元的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/world-bank-launches-program-to-boost-guarantees-by-20-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界银行启动了一项新计划，旨在到2020年将投资担保额提高到200亿美元，以调动数万亿美元的投资，为贫穷国家的发展和气候项目提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/world-bank-launches-program-to-boost-guarantees-by-20-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普豁免裁决意味着选举前的任何审判都不太可能</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/supreme-court-partially-backs-trump-on-immunity-delaying-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院周一裁定，唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 因其试图推翻 2020 年大选结果而免受部分刑事指控，这对检察官在 11 月大选前进行审判的努力造成了几乎致命的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/supreme-court-partially-backs-trump-on-immunity-delaying-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 14:34:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列命令巴勒斯坦人逃离汗尤尼斯，暗示可能发动新一轮袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-01/israel-releases-director-of-hospital-it-says-was-used-as-a-hamas-base-he-alleges-abuse-in-custody</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汗尤尼斯，加沙地带（美联社）——以色列军队周一下令巴勒斯坦人从汗尤尼斯大部分地区大规模撤离，这表明军队可能对加沙地带第二大城市发动新一轮地面攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-01/israel-releases-director-of-hospital-it-says-was-used-as-a-hamas-base-he-alleges-abuse-in-custody</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 08:35:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
